      "code_hash": "0588021a919edfb11d478d9d492b7f91",
      "outputs": [
        {
          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"marimo-devtypes\">marimo-dev.types</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">The data structures that represent a marimo project.\nEverything downstream \u2014 package building, documentation,\nbundling \u2014 is a traversal of these structures.</span>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Design principle: the data structure should make\nevery algorithm that operates on it obvious. If you find\nyourself filtering, re-parsing, or reaching around the\ntypes, the types are wrong.</span>\n<div class=\"language-python codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">Hierarchy</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">Config</span>          <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">read</span> <span class=\"n\">once</span><span class=\"p\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">threaded</span> <span class=\"n\">everywhere</span>\n    <span class=\"n\">Project</span>         <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">the</span> <span class=\"n\">whole</span> <span class=\"n\">thing</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">meta</span> <span class=\"o\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">modules</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">Meta</span>          <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"kn\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">pyproject.toml</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">init_extras</span>   <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"kn\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">_init.py</span> <span class=\"n\">to</span> <span class=\"n\">inject</span> <span class=\"n\">dunder</span> <span class=\"n\">to</span> <span class=\"n\">the</span> <span class=\"n\">init</span> <span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mf\">0.4.2</span><span class=\"p\">]</span>\n      <span class=\"n\">Module</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>      <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">one</span> <span class=\"n\">per</span> <span class=\"n\">notebook</span> <span class=\"n\">file</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">Import</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>    <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">statements</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">Const</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>     <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">constant</span> <span class=\"n\">assignments</span> <span class=\"kn\">from</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nn\">setup</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">Setup</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>     <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">other</span> <span class=\"n\">setup</span> <span class=\"n\">cell</span> <span class=\"n\">code</span>\n        <span class=\"n\">Export</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>    <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">decorated</span> <span class=\"n\">functions</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">classes</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">Param</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>   <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"n\">parameters</span> <span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"n\">inline</span> <span class=\"n\">docs</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">Method</span><span class=\"p\">[]</span>  <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"k\">class</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">methods</span> <span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"k\">if</span> <span class=\"n\">class</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n          <span class=\"n\">Return</span>    <span class=\"err\">\u2014</span> <span class=\"k\">return</span> <span class=\"n\">annotation</span> <span class=\"k\">with</span> <span class=\"n\">inline</span> <span class=\"n\">doc</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<span class=\"paragraph\"><strong>Note</strong>: <code>Import</code>, <code>Const</code>, <code>Setup</code>, and <code>Raw</code> only need source text.\nOnly <code>Export</code> needs the rich structure (params, methods, etc).</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
